Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:02.71,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.03,0:02:05.78,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What? What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.78,0:02:08.47,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.47,0:02:09.63,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.42,0:02:12.88,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're kidding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.49,0:02:30.76,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.77,0:02:31.68,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where did the shot come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:34.93,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.04,0:02:41.89,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mission accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.21,0:02:43.50,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:47.40,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Move to route C and await further orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.01,0:02:50.19,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:55.90,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A gun that didn't hit stirs up discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:03:01.15,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well then, how will the heroine improvise her escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.19,0:03:07.92,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is it proper manners to call a meeting and then suddenly start shooting?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.30,0:03:14.03,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You will pay for this, I swear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.03,0:03:16.45,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What the hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:18.69,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Didn't one of you shoot first?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:21.52,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:22.88,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:25.85,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll kill you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:28.18,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't, Mr. Godou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:31.36,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.98,0:03:48.66,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That startled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:57.82,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Lei...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:01.91,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.87,0:04:04.22,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:08.57,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:20.40,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's another sniper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.40,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:23.86,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:25.92,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, Reiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:28.28,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:29.93,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:31.68,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:38.45,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.16,0:04:43.51,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My subordinate has managed to neutralize the threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:46.24,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There will be no danger of another shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:49.73,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What kind of farce is this, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:51.07,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mr. Godou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:55.10,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He's responsible for stealing your money, threatening and attempting to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:58.35,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I present to you Isaac Wisemel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.35,0:04:59.77,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:04.55,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A traitor deep within the organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:06.61,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...has been disposed of by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:08.95,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Traitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.95,0:05:10.65,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can explain this, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.03,0:05:13.26,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sending one of our own to heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.26,0:05:14.78,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.78,0:05:18.67,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This sniping was plotted by Wisemel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:22.66,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My subordinate has discovered and incapacitated the sniper,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:25.15,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}which is evidence beyond doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:29.62,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hum, you're telling quite a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:33.86,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is Inferno's way of settling debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:42.94,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The shot at the hotel was after I killed Randy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:46.05,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm certain it wasn't one of Wisemel's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.10,0:05:50.04,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was a different sniper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:53.29,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That guy was probably working under Wisemel too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:56.05,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He's always had backup plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:06:01.88,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then why did the negotiations resume and why did the sniper go silent?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:05.44,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wasn't it Wisemel's objective to kill Daisuke Godou?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.07,0:06:10.04,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You sound as if you know the truth behind all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:12.59,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's kill or be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:14.91,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't care either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:19.89,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The sniper's true objective was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:24.17,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...to disrupt them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:27.04,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To put strife into their midst.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:33.28,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did they even anticipate Claudia would shoot Wisemel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:34.93,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:39.73,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This whole case is a scheme of Wisemel's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:43.74,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Therefore, Clau killed him based on her own judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.74,0:06:46.11,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't overanalyze.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:47.98,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We are only soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:51.29,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's no need to step beyond that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:58.82,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's as Lizzy said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:02.29,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We don't need to know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:07.60,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If this crime spree was indeed perpetrated by Wisemel,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.60,0:07:10.30,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}then it's obvious where the five million dollars should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.13,0:07:18.65,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The stolen money of the Godou clan will come from Wisemel's villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.32,0:07:21.95,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This will settle everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:25.92,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The deaths of the yakuza and avenging Judy's murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:27.67,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:32.93,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...my own self-deception.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:36.30,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:44.24,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:47.06,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No way that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:49.31,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...she's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:00.55,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, I heard a rumor...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.55,0:08:03.42,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...saying that Isaac of the Bloodies died.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:05.38,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:12.37,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The sniper you shot was his henchman, and also the one who killed Judy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.42,0:08:14.11,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:17.91,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then it's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:19.21,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:24.73,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:28.13,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By the way, how did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.76,0:08:30.83,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Training me into an assassin, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:36.71,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If it's fine with you, can I help with other assassinations too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.11,0:08:41.59,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The killing... is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:42.77,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:45.37,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:48.48,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then I'm just a nuisance now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.37,0:08:51.45,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:52.88,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:53.82,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:57.19,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I do have need of your cooking skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:08:58.55,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:00.51,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can be a cooking maid for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.71,0:09:01.97,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:04.41,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yahoo, I get to be a maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:06.50,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've always wanted to try being a maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:09.58,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Maid uniforms are soo cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:11.30,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You don't need to wear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.04,0:09:15.01,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh, I don't wear a uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:16.37,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:22.23,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't mind though, since I can stay beside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:27.42,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A marvelous report.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:31.82,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This subsumes the series of incidents were the plotting of Isaac Wisemel,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.23,0:09:35.93,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and the Godou clan will have to accept that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:37.80,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:42.37,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm amazed you were able to conclude this in such chaotic times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:51.00,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:56.09,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will let you take the place Isaac vacated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:09:57.41,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:10:02.29,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't disappoint me, Claudia McCunnen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:05.83,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:21.78,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Potential?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:22.86,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:25.44,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She has a rare resourcefulness about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:28.00,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can call it a talent if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:30.06,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Talent".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:33.00,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I heard the same word a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:37.49,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In other words, you want to train the girl into another hitman?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:39.69,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.69,0:10:41.85,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you cannot give rise to something...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:44.81,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You know what happens, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:47.35,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:52.39,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well then, let's see how skillful you can shape her to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:01.36,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There won't come a danger larger than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:04.33,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I should find an excuse and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:05.59,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...send her away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:22.50,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}However, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:26.76,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...feel at ease here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:40.44,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:42.57,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:44.94,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I might be back late, perhaps a day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:45.92,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.95,0:11:48.45,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I should have told you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:50.97,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, it's ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.97,0:11:52.31,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Have a nice trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:53.50,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:55.61,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:03.91,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You seem to have taken well to office work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:06.09,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You must be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:09.41,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How about doing this from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:11.28,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Perhaps it's suited for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.28,0:13:13.34,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's no need to put yourself in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:15.01,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This isn't the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:17.83,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's only the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.22,0:13:20.72,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What more do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.72,0:13:22.95,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Greed could be the end of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.85,0:13:30.25,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I know you won't find rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.98,0:13:34.09,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But be careful where you tread.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:37.43,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do I look that stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:40.46,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}At least let me warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:42.03,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's my hobby anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:52.13,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal, I don't really understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.13,0:13:53.78,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is the fruit...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:58.30,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:07.39,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:08.89,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're already back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:11.62,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal, where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:15.52,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You bought the right one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.07,0:14:22.93,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's tastier to cook chicken with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.14,0:14:28.43,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is it fine to leave it like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.54,0:14:32.69,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Leave it like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:41.83,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:43.14,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.80,0:14:49.48,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I... want to be your assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:52.30,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.68,0:14:54.30,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:57.90,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your feelings about not letting me be an assassin, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:02.47,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You understand the sorrow of being an assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.91,0:15:08.06,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I want to be able to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.06,0:15:10.37,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm weak and poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.41,0:15:14.45,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't do anything without help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:17.01,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want to stay like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:22.38,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal, you have so many paths you can walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:23.92,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can be anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:27.08,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why must you become an assassin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:29.80,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji, do you hate being an assassin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:30.40,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:34.49,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then, do you hate yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:36.48,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, I hate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:39.77,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I became a killer and can't stop being a killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:41.83,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I really hate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.61,0:15:44.73,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But, Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:47.74,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm already broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.74,0:15:49.85,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you want to be like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.27,0:15:56.97,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I-I'm sorry, Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.67,0:15:58.55,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.63,0:16:19.12,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal, I said too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:22.37,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.57,0:16:25.15,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I told the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:28.40,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't know how many have died because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.41,0:16:32.27,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I were not in this world, they would be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.27,0:16:35.33,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They could return to their lovers and family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:38.44,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.69,0:16:44.38,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Killing was just your duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:47.15,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not so simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:51.41,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then, do you wish to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:54.13,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did you kill because you wanted to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:55.90,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you like to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.73,0:17:01.57,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're different, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:06.81,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You feel hurt, pained and sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:09.61,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can't forgive yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.54,0:17:12.96,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You want to kill yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:19.29,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But unlike Judy's killer you don't shoot without reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:22.55,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're bearing the pain of living.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:24.63,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why you don't make mistakes, Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.63,0:17:26.71,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You won't kill people at random.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:31.92,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If those people had been like you, Reiji,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:35.32,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sure Judy wouldn't have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.67,0:17:40.58,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But, Cal,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:43.78,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}once you kill someone, the entire world changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:46.37,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even the sceneries you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:48.71,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...and the sounds that reach your ear...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:50.31,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:52.63,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The way you are now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:56.56,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You won't be able to accept kindness any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:17:59.33,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want you to be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.67,0:18:02.89,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This place was not meant for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:07.17,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You shouldn't come over to my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:09.09,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:13.11,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But you will always stay in that world, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:18.92,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I step into your world, I can be beside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.90,0:18:21.96,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:25.30,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want to be separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.30,0:18:27.38,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to stay beside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:30.61,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To be useful for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:35.30,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.36,0:18:38.41,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...together with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.87,0:18:42.05,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:43.82,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:50.99,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...wanted to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:19:00.01,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I could be with you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.92,0:19:02.30,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:04.02,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:08.40,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will come to your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.17,0:19:09.98,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:12.52,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let me go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:16.20,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...to Cal's world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:32.37,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal, before I met you, I was as good as dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.67,0:19:37.63,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If we're seperated...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:39.80,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...I would be the walking dead again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:44.09,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're the one who made me recall...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.09,0:19:46.29,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...how to laugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.29,0:19:47.53,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...and how to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:51.74,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What, it's him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.55,0:19:54.32,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:56.83,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.91,0:19:59.10,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's that kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:01.35,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was shocked as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:06.85,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ms. McCunnen should have been helping you join Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.69,0:20:10.39,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When did that change, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:12.19,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't fucking care.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.95,0:20:15.25,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Contact the boss immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.25,0:20:16.18,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:16.99,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:25.46,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your turn will soon be over, Ms. McCunnen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:30.10,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will gift you with a grand flower for the falling curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.43,0:20:35.29,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:38.07,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Phantom, can you move out now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:39.86,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is it so suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:43.99,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The Bloodies are making suspicious moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.99,0:20:46.46,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'd like it to be silently taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:48.52,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Could you do me the favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.46,0:20:50.41,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:51.82,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where should I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.44,0:20:55.55,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We will meet at the usual spot, and hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:20:56.79,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.68,0:21:08.94,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Job?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.94,0:21:09.66,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:13.06,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wanted to have the whole day with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.70,0:21:15.07,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.07,0:21:17.93,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We will always be together from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.60,0:21:19.46,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.74,0:21:22.67,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:36.13,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll return to my old self.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.62,0:21:43.64,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}For Cal's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.94,0:21:47.35,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:51.66,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...for Elen's as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.34,0:23:36.94,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't call me Elen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.70,0:23:38.99,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.88,0:23:43.04,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}From the days of yore until now, simply Ein.
